One of the most peaceful places i have been to when I visited at Sunrise but i heard many people say that they could never see the view. Try going at Sunrise to have a better chance at exploring its true beauty.

Its located around 30 kms from Shillong. Takes around 1h30 mins by bike, so leave accordingly 🙌

Share with someone who should go here 🙌
